Class Constant.SharedPreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.focusnet.app.util.Constant.SharedPreferences
  • Enclosing class:
    Constant

    public static final class Constant.SharedPreferences
extends java.lang.Object
    SharedPreferences contain basic information for logging in and starting the application when no network is available.
